{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/y1kre1w7","slide":2,"text":"Strong models are valuable - but using them for every task is wasteful.","textPreview":"Strong models are valuable - but using them for every task is wasteful.","textChars":71,"textLines":1,"bbox":[54,80,1160,112]}
